title: Kingdom Rush
description:
Dressed the role of a noble and heroic warrior in a fantastic game of defense turrets full of spectacular animations. His Majesty the King Denas required your intervention to protect the population from attacks by bandits, outlaws and frightening creatures. Bring your army on the battlefield to strengthen the defenses of the city. Make sure that the enemy does not surpass the entry point of your kingdom and keep them away, stopping once and for all their expansionist ambitions. 
He played with the mouse. Place towers along the path of the route to protect the city, you will earn gold for every enemy soldier killed. You will need to produce and strengthen new types of defensive towers. Premium content and all the heroes sbloccat
